[The citation of the article referenced above follows:
Zhao M, Woodside MT. Mechanical strength of RNA knot in Zika virus protects against cellular defenses. Nat Chem Biol. 2021; https://doi.org/10.1038/s41589-021-00829-z.

This report provides insights into the biophysical characteristics of Zika virus RNA that render it resistant to the proteases that would otherwise degrade it. - Mod.TY]
